data.description: Newly renovated residence situated on an expansive lot, located just east of Irvington at the cul-de-sac's end. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts two distinct living areas and a generously sized dining space within its modernized kitchen. Experience the luxury of newer windows, roof, kitchen appliances, water heater, flooring, and bathrooms throughout. Unpack and immediately relish the spacious patio or take a stroll to explore the vibrant offerings of Irvington. Ample storage space is available, including a private workshop at the rear of the property. The family room features vaulted ceilings adorned with exposed beams, creating a captivating ambiance. With no homeowners association (HOA),  All appliances are included, providing a move-in-ready and effortlessly enjoyable living experience.
